85. List the steps to get file name from a path in PHP.
•	Use basename($path) → returns file name
•	Use pathinfo($path) → returns array (dirname, basename, extension, filename)
<?php
$path = "/var/www/html/example.txt";
echo basename($path) . "<br>";   // example.txt
echo pathinfo($path, PATHINFO_FILENAME); // example
?>
